rComments: Dr. Kramer is retiring this year and it's a huge loss to the department (but she's earned it!). She is extremely knowledgeable about a wide variety of topics in her discipline, and makes the lectures fun and interesting. I'm a science student and still got a ton out of this course!

Professor Kramer is incredibly intelligent and truly is an authority on this subject.  Uoft is lucky to have her! Her lectures are really interesting and she is funny, animated, and a joy to listen to.  She also memorizes every name in her class and will remember you afterwards which is always heart-warming.
Really enthusiastic and funny, my favourite prof so far. Occasionally absent-minded, but makes the class and material very fun and teaches it well. Great prof.
